          "en": "My mindset is Strong Mentality"
        },
        "description": {
          "ko": "스트레스와 실패를 빠르게 극복하는 타입",
          "en": "You recover quickly from stress and setbacks"
        },
        "image": "/images/quiz/mental-strength-test/result-1.webp"
      }
    },
